E.Soukhovitskii and R. Capote
Nucl. Data Sheets 110 (2009) 3107-3214 (RIPL paper)
Lane-consistent dispersive CC proton OMP for incident energies between 1 keV
and 200 MeV for Zr isotopes. Recommended for Zr-90,92,94,96. Local Fermi energy
used. See 609 for neutron OMP. Soft rotor. See RIPL paper, Table 6.
Following paper E = Ep - 1.1 * Z/A**1/3.
